 '"'||v3.day_name||'"', v3.year, v3.month_number, v3.day_number,
 '"'||v4.fare_id||'"', '"'||v5.flight_id||'"',
 v5.departure_time, '"'||v6.airport_code||'"', '"'||v7.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v7.city_name||'"', '"'||v8.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v9.city_code||'"', '"'||v9.city_name||'"', '"'||v10.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v11.day_name||'"', v11.year, v11.month_number,
 v11.day_number FROM fare v0, fare_basis v1, days v2, date_day v3,
 flight_fare v4, flight v5, airport_service v6, city v7,
 airport_service v8, city v9, days v10, date_day v11 
WHERE (((v0.fare_basis_code = ANY v1.fare_basis_code) AND ((v1.basis_days = ANY v2.days_code) 
AND ((v2.day_name = ANY v3.day_name) 
AND (((v3.year =  1993) AND (v3.month_number =  5)) 
AND (v3.day_number =  17))))) AND ((v0.fare_id = ANY v4.fare_id) 
AND ((v4.flight_id = ANY v5.flight_id) AND ((v5.departure_time BETWEEN  0 
AND  1200) AND (((v5.from_airport = ANY v6.airport_code) 
AND ((v6.city_code = ANY v7.city_code) 
AND (v7.city_name = 'NEW YORK'))) AND (((v5.to_airport = ANY v8.airport_code) 
AND ((v8.city_code = ANY v9.city_code) AND (v9.city_name = 'LOS ANGELES'))) 
AND ((v5.flight_days = ANY v10.days_code) 
AND ((v10.day_name = ANY v11.day_name) AND (((v11.year =  1993) 
AND (v11.month_number =  5)) AND (v11.day_number =  17))))))))));
